history.proof: intros a b l H. induction l as [|x xs IH]. - simpl. contradiction. - simpl. destruct (Aeq_dec b x) as [eq | neq]. + hauto lq: on depth: 3. + hauto lq: on depth: 3.

exceptions.exn: Wrong bullet +: Current bullet + is not finished.

original: intros a b l H. induction l as [|x xs IH]. - simpl. intro. contradiction. - simpl. intro. destruct (Aeq_dec b x) as [eq | neq]. + now left. + right. apply IH. intro. apply H. right. apply H0.
